data.description: THIS HOME IS ASSUMABLE!  ASSUME THE SELLERS CURRENT LOAN AT 2.375% INTEREST RATE WITH AS LITTLE AS 10% DOWN PAYMENT!  Adorable 3 bed, 2-bath home with tons of charm! This home is tastefully decorated in a neutral color palette and sets a calm and peaceful tone, enhanced by the  wood-look flooring throughout. The eat-in kitchen is equipped with modern SS appliances, a convenient pantry and trendy island, with french doors leading to the backyard. A nicely sized master bedroom that includes a private bathroom for privacy and ease. The meticulously designed backyard, offers a covered patio, low-maintenance artificial turf, a storage shed that is currently used as a work shop, and a gazebo with a built-in BBQ, ready for weekend grilling and memorable gatherings. New A/C in 2020.  The roof was resealed in 202and offers transferrable warranty.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your new home.
